title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sightseeing - 5 UK cities prior to World update 3
description:
In this video we will have a look at the 5 cities in the UK which will be upgraded as part of World update 3. Yesterday evening during the Twitch broadcast from Asobo it was announced that Bristol, Birmingham, Cambridge, London and Oxford will receive an update. This in addition to the other scenery enhancements which will be made.
